data.description: Welcome to 616 Buckingham Drive, a stunning house that is now available for sale. This spacious property features 4-5 bedrooms and 4 full baths, providing ample space for comfortable living.   Step inside and you'll be greeted by a range of modern updates. In 2017, a new pool, roof, oil tank, and holding water tank were installed, ensuring peace of mind for the new owners. The outside HVAC unit was also replaced in 2017, while the indoor HVAC unit was updated in 2023.  This house boasts a variety of desirable amenities, including a mini bar in the basement for entertaining guests. The master bedroom comes complete with a new en suite bath and a conveniently located laundry area within the walk-in closet.   Outside, you'll find a large yard that offers plenty of space for outdoor activities. Enjoy cooking and entertaining? The outdoor kitchen and fireplace are perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends. Additionally, an above-ground pool is available for those seeking relief from the summer heat.  Located in a water privilege community, this property provides access to various waterfront activities that are sure to enhance your lifestyle.  With 8 parking spaces available, there's no need to worry about finding parking for your vehicles or accommodating guests.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own this beautiful house on Buckingham Drive. Contact us today to schedule a showing and make this property your dream home!
